data.subject: Fwd: Offer Letter from 3I INFOTECH BPO LTD
data.body:
*Dear Mr. Shekhar Priyadarshi,*

We are happy to welcome you on-board at 3I INFOTECH BPO LTD.

We would like to introduce ourselves as HR Operations Team who will be
always ready to serve you in all relevant HR Assistance.

We undertake certain activities of employee on-boarding process using
online portal. Please find below access details and your login credentials
for offer acceptance.

Site URL https://implement.diyhr.in/3IINFOTECH-SS/Candidate/Login
Username shekhar.priyadarshi@gmail.com
Password 09115811

The portal usage is easy and intuitive to use. We request you to login and
complete updating your profile. Portal allows you to go through various
company policies.

We have also attached company offer letter for your reference and we wish
you best of luck for future assignments and a rewarding career at 3I
INFOTECH BPO LTD.

For further assistance/any queries contact details are mentioned below for
your ready reference.


Best Regards,
Team HR
